{"tid":708112,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"傳胎死腹中 iPhone SE2 今年不會現身","createTime":"2018-06-19T05:55:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-19T11:12:45.000Z","uid":32577,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"1c0b690abf6b4c8c6a0fc65e2fa412254696ff51","tid":708112,"uid":32577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T05:55:10.000Z","msg":"在 WWDC 2018 舉行之前，版主虎仔跟大家分享了不少有關 iPhone SE2 的新聞，坦白說版主亦為之心動，準備推出時入手一部自用。可惜在 WWDC 的發佈會未見 iPhone SE2 的影蹤，昨日讓人失望的消息傳出，iPhone SE2 今年內都不會發表。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n著名手機配件生產商 Olixar 昨日表示，iPhone SE 2 已經被 Apple 取消，這家爆出 iPhone SE 2 設計的配件生產商，指 Apple 將會把焦點放在 6.1 和 6.5 吋大螢幕的 iPhone，前者售價相對便宜，後者則屬於旗艦機種，擁有較佳的規格和最新的 Face ID 2.0。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n除了 Olixar 流出 iPhone SE 2 的手機保護殼產品照，著名爆料人 @OnLeaks 亦曾經上載過手機的 CAD 設計圖，相信手機真實存在，只是 Apple 臨門一腳決定取消，或者將它延期推出。<br />\n<br />\n資料來源：gsmarena<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.eprice.com.hk/mobile/talk/4544/210870\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.eprice.com.hk%2Fmobile%2Ftalk%2F4544%2F210870&d=hGdvfP6cD8H6T5SaF5jJTfiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=7b86a9b4\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.eprice.com.hk/mobile/talk/4544/210870</a>/<br />\n&nbsp;"},{"pid":"0a7f558abb1109f566f174c8e3130967dff50d50","tid":708112,"uid":32577,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T05:55:43.000Z","msg":"molamola,本來想買部做後備機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28355add3c40fd3a872ac9f1adf7417a1f135efd","tid":708112,"uid":1714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T06:07:14.000Z","msg":"clickbait eprice 不了"},{"pid":"0f57dd0ea426203dd74d08d733d9bd221f1f5a66","tid":708112,"uid":8014,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T06:53:10.000Z","msg":"正仆街 迫我考古買ip8<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08c68c94f692a49d2c1d75528708c400c054d7f3","tid":708112,"uid":3241,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T07:43:40.000Z","msg":"越